== The install depends on your version of Mac OS ==

For Mac OS Snow Leopard (10.6) or Lion (10.7) or Mountain Lion (10.8):

* Install this DMG: [https://git-osx-installer.googlecode.com/files/git-1.8.0.2-intel-universal-snow-leopard.dmg https://git-osx-installer.googlecode.com/files/git-1.8.0.2-intel-universal-snow-leopard.dmg]

For other versions of Mac OS:

* Go through this [http://code.google.com/p/git-osx-installer/downloads/list long list of options] and pick the one best-suited to your computer. If you're not sure, ask an instructor.

